node.text:
Episode 6 of @welcometofriday.pod is live. We have 3 new sketches, and talk a lot about how Adam Duritz dated Jennifer Aniston, Christina Applegate, Courtney Cox, and Emmy Rossum.

Written by @maxwellredington @jbfresh2

Sketch timecodes:

0:00 - A Sneaky Bender (Counting Crows cover)
6:54 - Friday Women of Beerness: Ms. Terrified Emotional Support Dog Haver
9:10 - Doctor’s Appointment (featuring Eric Griffin and Kirk Fox)
16:23 - NPR Presents: The Consumption Vortex

Thank you to @allthingscomedy @erikgriffin @kirkfox  @jimmyblueberry @bencahn @courtneypauroso @_mallorykm_
